        <briefdescription>
<para>Runs every DispatchingRule on an instance and returns results sorted by makespan. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Iterates all values of the DispatchingRule enum via <computeroutput>Enum.GetValues</computeroutput>, delegates each to <ref refid="class_assets_1_1_scripts_1_1_scheduling_1_1_validation_1_1_validation_runner_1acc29f6fc8de3820b1229ea52786a8c68" kindref="member">RunSingle</ref>, and sorts the collected results by <ref refid="struct_assets_1_1_scripts_1_1_scheduling_1_1_validation_1_1_validation_runner_1_1_validation_result_1a1b4e8e889bb4876f00515d4376cbcf92" kindref="member">ValidationResult.Makespan</ref> ascending so the best-performing heuristic appears first. Useful for identifying the strongest baseline rule for a given instance before applying RL-based scheduling.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>instance</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The benchmark instance to run all rules against.</para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="return"><para>A list of <ref refid="struct_assets_1_1_scripts_1_1_scheduling_1_1_validation_1_1_validation_runner_1_1_validation_result" kindref="compound">ValidationResult</ref> values, one per DispatchingRule, sorted by makespan ascending. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
