    <briefdescription>
<para>Validates the DESSimulator against Taillard JSP benchmark instances. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Provides three levels of validation:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para><ref refid="class_assets_1_1_scripts_1_1_scheduling_1_1_validation_1_1_validation_runner_1acc29f6fc8de3820b1229ea52786a8c68" kindref="member">RunSingle</ref> — simulate one instance with one DispatchingRule and measure the gap to optimum.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para><ref refid="class_assets_1_1_scripts_1_1_scheduling_1_1_validation_1_1_validation_runner_1a8024432bea5a9a1908488f3611bd2efd" kindref="member">RunAllRules</ref> — sweep every DispatchingRule and return results sorted by makespan.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para><ref refid="class_assets_1_1_scripts_1_1_scheduling_1_1_validation_1_1_validation_runner_1a68a76d37888dd4b0aaadc15867c029b9" kindref="member">ValidateConstraints</ref> — verify correctness invariants (valid times, precedence, no machine overlap, makespan above lower bound).</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<para>Usage outside <ref refid="namespace_assets_1_1_scripts_1_1_scheduling_1_1_unity" kindref="compound">Unity</ref>: <programlisting><codeline><highlight class="normal">var<sp/>runner<sp/>=<sp/></highlight><highlight class="keyword">new</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>ValidationRunner();</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">runner.RunValidation(taillardInstance);</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
<para>Usage inside <ref refid="namespace_assets_1_1_scripts_1_1_scheduling_1_1_unity" kindref="compound">Unity</ref>: <programlisting><codeline><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Call<sp/>from<sp/>a<sp/>MonoBehaviour<sp/>via<sp/>the<sp/>TaillardValidator<sp/>component.</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting> </para>
    </detaileddescription>
